description: Anastacia - The Video collection [2002] DVD9 Anastacia Lyn Newkirk (born September 17, 1968) is an American singer-songwriter, producer and former dancer. She is best known for her electric pop music of the early 2000s which had a significant impact in Europe and Oceania. Her first two albums Not That Kind (2000) and Freak of Nature (2001) were released in quick succession to major success. This collection includes all the videos of Anastacia from her two albums - "Not That Kind" and "Freak Of Nature", as well as a clip on the song "Boom - 2002 FIFA World Cup". The DVD is a compilation of ten music videos, released on December 2, 2002.
